5, \"to\": 1301}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That race was a thriller, the USA heavy favourites after breaking the world record on Friday but denied by one of the all-time great anchor legs from Dutch superstar Femke Bol.\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1479, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1333, \"end\": 1336, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9965449369936863, \"rank\": 0.003456434102848104, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1453, \"end\": 1458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9093316560691597, \"rank\": 0.09683070151185988, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}, {\"begin\": 1469, \"end\": 1478, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Femke_Bol\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Femke Bol\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Femke_Bol\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Femke_Bol\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That race\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1312}, {\"ngram\": \"a thriller\", \"from\": 1317, \"to\": 1327}, {\"ngram\": \"the world record\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1385}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1395}, {\"ngram\": \"the all-time great anchor legs\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1447}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This, though, was Alfred's true breakthrough, hardly a shock after a stellar season to now, but still a first global medal outdoors.\", \"from\": 1481, \"to\": 1613, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Alfred's true breakthrough\", \"from\": 1499, \"to\": 1525}, {\"ngram\": \"hardly a shock\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1541}, {\"ngram\": \"a stellar season\", \"from\": 1548, \"to\": 1564}, {\"ngram\": \"still a first global medal