 \"from\": 1861, \"to\": 1871}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Richardson was already established as the brilliant, brash rising star of the sprint scene when forced out of Tokyo after testing positive for THC, the primary ingredient in cannabis, which she took to help manage grief after her mother's passing while trying to qualify for the Games.\", \"from\": 1874, \"to\": 2159, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1874, \"end\": 1884, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.396064223771634e-15, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}, {\"begin\": 1984, \"end\": 1989, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9828993662973907, \"rank\": 0.017398153022945444, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 2017, \"end\": 2020, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tetrahydrocannabinol\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.519069694058612e-22, \"text\": \"THC\", \"types\": [\"Q8386\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tetrahydrocannabinol\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tetrahydrocannabinol\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the brilliant, brash rising star\", \"from\": 1912, \"to\": 1944}, {\"ngram\": \"the sprint scene\", \"from\": 1948, \"to\": 1964}, {\"ngram\": \"the primary ingredient\", \"from\": 2022, \"to\": 2044}, {\"ngram\": \"cannabis\", \"from\": 2048, \"to\": 2056}, {\"ngram\": \"grief\", \"from\": 2088, \"to\": 2093}, {\"ngram\": \"her mother's passing\", \"from\": 2100, \"to\": 2120}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2149, \"to\": 2158}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alfred's absence, through an injury that wiped out her season, was less newsworthy, but came following an indoor season in which her promise had just begun to make the odd wave on the American collegiate scene.\", \"from\": 2161, \"to\": 2371, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2345, \"end\": 2353, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999836309145, \"rank\": 9.798789593742726e-09, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Alfred's absence\", \"from\": 2161, \"to\": 2177}, {\"ngram\": \"an injury\", \"from\": 2187, \"to\": 2196}, {\"ngram\": \"her season\", \"from\": 2212, \"to\": 2222}, {\"ngram\": \"an indoor season\", \"from\": 2264, \"to\": 2280}, {\"ngram\": \"her promise\", \"from\": 2290, \"to\": 2301}, {\"ngram\": \"the odd wave\", \"from\": 2325, \"to\": 2337}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She had grown up idolising Usain Bolt - and watched re-runs of his Olympic finals as preparation this morning - but was in danger of drifting away from athletics after the death of her father while aged just 12.\", \"from\": 2373, \"to\": 2584, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2400, \"end\": 2410, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Usain_Bolt\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Usain Bolt\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Usain_Bolt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Usain_Bolt\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"runs\", \"from\": 2428, \"to\": 2432}, {\"ngram\": \"his Olympic finals\", \"from\": 2436, \"to\": 2454}, {\"ngram\": \"preparation\", \"from\": 2458, \"to\": 2469}, {\"ngram\": \"danger\", \"from\": 2496, \"to\": 2502}, {\"ngram\": \"athletics\", \"from\": 2525, \"to\": 2534}, {\"ngram\": \"the death\", \"from\": 2541, \"to\": 2550}, {\"ngram\": \"her father\", \"from\": 2554, \"to\": 2564}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In December last year, Simeon Stephen, the PE teacher at her secondary school in Castries she credits with spotting her talent and keeping her quite literally on the track, passed away, too.\", \"from\": 2585, \"to\": 2775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2608, \"end\": 2614, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shimon_bar_Yochai\", \"score\": 0.9876717303982566, \"rank\": 0.009302552115040703, \"text\": \"Simeon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q2566598\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shimon_bar_Yochai\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shimon_bar_Yochai\"}, {\"begin\": 2628, \"end\": 2630, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Physical_education\", \"score\": 0.9999999999790816, \"rank\": 1.6890810845964936e-11, \"text\": \"PE\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Physical_education\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Physical_education\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"December\", \"from\": 2588, \"to\": 2596}, {\"ngram\": \"her secondary school\", \"from\": 2642, \"to\": 2662}, {\"ngram\": \"Castries\", \"from\": 2666, \"to\": 2674}, {\"ngram\": \"her talent\", \"from\": 2701, \"to\": 2711}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 2747, \"to\": 2756}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tonight, in the St. Lucian capital, they will celebrate hard, but will not be alone.\", \"from\": 2777, \"to\": 2861, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2797, \"end\": 2803, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\", \"score\": 0.9999027161068735, \"rank\": 9.729335799073625e-05, \"text\": \"Lucian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Remarkably, 20 minutes later, Dominica also claimed their first ever Olympic medal, and that, too, an athletics gold, delivered by Thea Lafond in the women's triple jump.\", \"from\": 2862, \"to\": 3032, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2892, \"end\": 2900, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dominica\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.066286762875199e-